{"tid":608327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"虛報日本駐港總領事館失火及有炸彈 思覺失調男獲無條件釋放","createTime":"2018-03-28T05:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T07:54:13.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"14577739c57b2971d1dfd717fa411b2a982fae1a","tid":608327,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180328/large/1522211191_f45e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180328%2Flarge%2F1522211191_f45e.jpg&h=1e7eb148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告溫炎祥(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n患思覺失調症18年的男子去年2月，分別致電999報案中心及1823政府熱線謊稱日本駐港總領事館失火及有炸彈，反恐特遣隊及港島衝鋒隊到場證實全屬虛驚。男子事後被捕，聲稱因日本否認侵華史實心存反感，潛意識驅使兼精神病發，失控下才說了該些話。他早前就浪費警力及向他人傳達有炸彈的虛假消息兩罪受審，鑑於男子的精神狀況，未能證明其犯罪意圖，裁判官今裁定他無條件釋放。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官曾先後索閱被告的精神科醫生及社會福利機構報告，以了解是否需要判被告溫炎祥（31歲）入院令或接受社署監管。報告指被告毋須入院，但需接受門診式精神治療，由於被告病情穩定，亦得到家人支持及照顧，毋須社署監管。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180328/58004766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F58004766&d=TC3XDdTJI0SOQiMG3%2Fy3h2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=f43d7d63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F58004766&h=3a57c915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180328/58004766</a>"},{"pid":"69c4d6ae237347a826c5444acb992318fb6fa4ef","tid":608327,"uid":41508,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fde4addbb0fddfe79947a8c52180586ca806a0f","tid":608327,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69c4d6ae237347a826c5444acb992318fb6fa4ef","tid":608327,"uid":41508,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"